1. Find your wireless interface name.
By default all configuraiton file has "wlan0".
But if its something else, use following command to change it in all configuration files necessary

# change_wireless_interface.sh <new interface name>

2. Edit /etc/network/interface and add your wifi credentials

3. Reboot

4. See /var/log/syslog for zipgateway logs

 or restart gateway to see it on the console

 # /etc/init.d/zipgateway stop
 # /etc/init.d/zipgateway start 
